'''Ali Reza Ashrafi''' is an [[Iran]]ian [[mathematician]] who works in [[computational group theory]] and [[mathematical chemistry]]. Ashrafi is a professor of the Department of mathematics of University of Kashan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=hqM116QAAAAJ&hl=en|access-date=2018-07-02 |title=Ali Reza Ashrafi profile at Google Scholar |website=[[Google Scholar]]}}</ref><ref name="Resume">{{Cite web|url=http://ashrafi.faculty.kashanu.ac.ir/en/Index.html |title=Alireza Ashrafi|website=[[University of Kashan]] |access-date=2018-07-02}}</ref>

