In the [[United Kingdom]], the '''Government Operational Research Service''' (GORS) supports and champions [[Operational Research]] across government. GORS currently supports policy-making, strategy and operations in many different departments and agencies across the United Kingdom and employs around 500 analysts, ranging from sandwich students to members of the Senior Civil Service.<ref>[http://www.operational-research.gov.uk/recruitment/ GORS Homepage]</ref>
